  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bbe\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b92\u0bb0\u0bc1 \u0b87\u0bb2\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bc1 \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb2\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0bb0\u0bcb \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0ba9 \u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Litro company leader to market one lakh gas cylinders daily in coming days",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "We have fulfilled our promise to the people of the country that we will bring gas supply to normal in a phased manner. In the coming days, one lakh gas cylinders will be distributed to the market daily, said Muditha Peiris, Chairman of Litro.",
        "We are happy to announce that we have fulfilled our promise to the people of the country to restore gas supply in a phased manner. About 20 lakh gas cylinders have been supplied to the market in the last month alone.",
        "We have decided to distribute 1 lakh gas cylinders to the market daily in the future. Also, it must be noted that there will be no impact on the gas supply structure for the next 4 months.",
        "Consumers should avoid buying gas cylinders at high prices in the black market. We have urged the appropriate parties to take legal action against the parties selling gas cylinders at high prices, he said."
      ],
